<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs>  with lid (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">2.275</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">1.545</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">1.11</measure>), decorated with three <rs type="decoration">garland</rs>s with <rs type="decoration">bust</rs>s between, and two standing <rs type="decoration">figure</rs>s below; for fuller description see bibliography.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>It was once <rs type="execution" key="scalpro">inscribed</rs> along the edge of the lid, along the upper front edge of the box and on either side of the busts, but the texts have been carefully erased, leaving only a few letters along the front edge.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre" precision="circa">0.02-0.03</measure>. Lunate sigma.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0300" notBefore="0201" exact="none">Third century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="1"/>  <gap reason="lost" extent="3" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">ΑΛΩ</orig>  <gap reason="lost" extent="6" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">σο<unclear reason="damage">γ</unclear></orig>  <gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">οκλι</orig></ab>
</div>

